OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice for students
OL,6,FStudents at the University of Kent in
OL,7,FCanterbury are being urged to remain
OL,8,Fvigilant for the signs of meningitis
OL,9,Fand sepsis, following an outbreak over
OL,10,Fthe weekend.
OL,12,FTwo people have died and several more
OL,13,Fare in hospital, following an outbreak
OL,14,Fof an "invasive" disease.
OL,16,FThose affected are believed to be
OL,17,Fstudents at the university, and all
OL,18,Fcases have been reported between
OL,19,FFriday (13 March) and Sunday (15
OL,20,FMarch).
OL,26,@vD@GOUvD@PO]
