OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice for students
OL,6,FStudents who are unwell should call
OL,7,FNHS 111 or their GP, or if they are
OL,8,Fseriously unwell, go to their nearest
OL,9,FEmergency Department.
OL,11,FITV Meridian understands antibiotics
OL,12,Fwill be offered to students on campus
OL,13,Fon Monday 16 March.
OL,15,FWhat are the symptoms of meningitis or
OL,16,Fsepsis?
OL,18,FThey can include:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
