FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773668266
OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice for students
OL,6,F"That's why it's vital that, if a
OL,7,Ffriend goes to bed unwell, you check
OL,8,Fon them regularly and don't hesitate
OL,9,Fto seek medical help by contacting
OL,10,Ftheir GP or calling NHS 111 if they
OL,11,Fhave these symptoms, or you're
OL,12,Fconcerned about them. This could save
OL,13,Ftheir life."
OL,15,FWhat is the advice for students at the
OL,16,FUniversity of Kent?
OL,18,FAt the moment, students who are well
OL,19,Fin themselves should listen out for
OL,20,Fupdates from the NHS and the
OL,21,FUniversity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@LO]
