PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773668266
OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of meningitis
OL,4,Cand what is the advice for students
OL,6,FClose contacts of people who have been
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with the disease have been
OL,8,Fgiven antibiotics already, and health
OL,9,Fbosses say they are monitoring the
OL,10,Fsituation closely.
OL,12,FIf you are unwell, NHS 111 is open 24
OL,13,Fhours a day, and will be able to
OL,14,Fadvise on what to do.
OL,16,FPeople who feel fine, and have no
OL,17,Fsymptoms, should not attend hospital.
OL,18,FThe NHS says this could delay
OL,19,Ftreatments for those who really need
OL,20,Fit, and put pressure on the system.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
